---
title: Pesto Chicken Burger and Bacon Baby Potatoes with balsamic salad
description: This Italian-inspired burger features a moreish pesto mayo, tangy balsamic salad, and, perhaps best of all, golden crumbed chicken breast sandwiched between two beautiful brioche buns. As if that's not enough, smashed cheesy bacon baby potatoes round out the dish.
